== 旅游和签证 ==
[[File:Visa_requirements_for_Lithuanian_citizens.png|thumb]]的{{link-en|立陶宛護照|Lithuanian passport}}之[[立陶宛人口|立陶宛公民]]可以[[簽證#签证优惠待遇|免簽證]]的方式入境[[巴西|巴西]]。]]
[[File:Visa_requirements_for_Brazilian_citizens.png|thumb]]的[[巴西人|巴西公民]]可以免签证入境[[立陶宛|立陶宛]]。]]
{{see also|歐洲聯盟簽證政策|立陶宛公民簽證要求}}
{{see also|巴西簽證政策|巴西公民簽證要求}}
歐洲[[申根區|申根區]]給予持[[巴西護照|巴西護照]]的[[巴西人|巴西公民]][[歐洲聯盟簽證政策|申根區免簽證]]待遇，停留日數與申根區合併計算，每6個月期間內總計可停留90天。<ref name = "Reg 610/2013">Article 1 of Regulation (EU) No 610/2013 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 26 June 2013 amending Regulation (EC) No 562/2006 of the European Parliament and of the Council establishing a Community Code on the rules governing the movement of persons across borders (Schengen Borders Code), the Convention implementing the Schengen Agreement, Council Regulations (EC) No 1683/95 and (EC) No 539/2001 and Regulations (EC) No 767/2008 and (EC) No 810/2009 of the European Parliament and of the Council ([http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=OJ:L:2013:182:0001:0018:EN:PDF OJ L 182, 29 June 2013, p. 1] {{Wayback|url=http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=OJ:L:2013:182:0001:0018:EN:PDF |date=20140209191815 }})</ref>

[[立陶宛人口|立陶宛公民]]持有[[歐盟護照|歐盟護照]]者也可以[[簽證#签证优惠待遇|免簽證]]的方式入境巴西，停留最多90天。<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=LT|destination=BR}}</ref>

== 文化交流 ==
[[Image:VilaZelina.jpg|thumb]]

2001年，巴西导演Fabiano Canosa和Julius Ziz拍摄了一部名为《黄金国：巴西的立陶宛人》([[葡萄牙语|葡萄牙语]]: Eldorado: Lituanos no Brasil)的纪录片，讲述了立陶宛人在巴西的移民史。<ref>{{Cite news | url= https://www.kviff.com/en/programme/film/4418283-eldorado-lithuanians-in-brazil-1924-29/ | title= Eldorado, Lithuanians in Brazil (1924-29) / Eldorado, os lituanos no Brasil (1924-29) | publisher= kviff.com |date=2020-09-20}}</ref>

在圣保罗的立陶宛人移民村，立陶宛的美食被保留下来，此外，[[复活节|复活节]]仍然以立陶宛的传统方式庆祝，立陶宛人制作的[[复活节彩蛋|复活节彩蛋]]也较有名气。

